        description: 'Upgrade to higher-tier plans to unlock more features and benefits for an enhanced experience.',
        icon: 'tabler:chevrons-up',
      },
      {
        title: '24H support',
        description: 'Questions answered via live chat, email or phone, every calendar day.',
        icon: 'tabler:headset',
      },
    ]}
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-5xl' }}
  />-->

  <!-- Steps Widget ****************** -->

  <Steps
    title="A guided journey from plans to creativity"
    tagline="simplified process"
    isReversed={true}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Sign Up',
        icon: 'tabler:number-1',
      },
      {
        title: 'Complete Onboarding',
        icon: 'tabler:number-2',
      },
      {
        title: 'Create an Oasis',
        icon: 'tabler:number-3',
      },
      {
        title: 'Invite Partners',
        icon: 'tabler:number-4',
      },
      {
        title: 'Share Leads',
        icon: 'tabler:number-5',
      },
      {
        title: 'See the results!',
        icon: 'tabler:number-6',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3876399/pexels-photo-3876399.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2',
      alt: 'Steps image',
    }}
  />

  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    title="Pricing FAQs"
    subtitle="Choosing the right plan is important, and we're here to answer your questions. If you have queries about our pricing options, you're in the right place."
    columns={1}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Do the plans come with customer support?',
        description:
          'Yes, all of our plans come with 24/7 customer support. You can contact us via live chat, email or phone, and we will be happy to assist you.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Is there a trial period?',
        description:
          "We don't offer a trial period, but we do have a free plan that you can use for as long as you like. You can also upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time.",
      },
      {
        title: 'Can I bring my existing toolstack?',
        description:
          'Yes, you can integrate your existing tools with our platform. We also offer a range of integrations that you can use to enhance your experience.',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- CallToAction Widget *********** -->

  <CallToAction
    title="Ready to boost your partner operations?"
    id="pricing-cta"
    subtitle="Get started today and see the results for yourself"
    actions={[
      {
        variant: 'primary',
        text: 'Join the waitlist',
        href: 'https://forms.fillout.com/t/bHn1ZhE6oLus',
      },
    ]}
  />
</Layout>
